net.dean.jraw.pagination

Class SearchPaginator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.pagination.Paginator<Submission>
      • net.dean.jraw.pagination.SearchPaginator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<Listing<Submission>>, NetworkAccessible<RedditResponse,RedditClient>

    public class SearchPaginator
extends Paginator<Submission>
    This class allows access to Reddit's search functionality. This class uses a special enum for sorting the values retrieved called SearchPaginator.SearchSort. To set this new sorting, use setSearchSorting(SearchSort).
